---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Pawly — Fair Care for Your Best Friend"
  description="Dog boarding with transparent pricing, vetted caregivers, and fees that don't punish loyalty. Pawly takes 12% — not 40% like Rover or Wag."
>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO
  ════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[88vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Layered warm gradient background -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 10% 60%, oklch(0.73 0.17 62 / 0.14), transparent 55%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 85% 15%, oklch(0.78 0.16 64 / 0.10), transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 55% 95%, oklch(0.87 0.12 68 / 0.12), transparent 45%),
      linear-gradient(160deg, oklch(0.987 0.012 78) 0%, oklch(0.966 0.015 76) 100%);
    "></div>

    <!-- Decorative floating elements -->
    <div class="absolute top-16 right-6 md:right-20 text-7xl md:text-9xl animate-float select-none opacity-20 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true">🐶</div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-20 left-4 md:left-16 text-4xl md:text-6xl animate-float select-none opacity-20 pointer-events-none" style="animation-delay:2.5s" aria-hidden="true">🐾</div>

    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 md:py-28">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">

        <!-- Badge -->
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-brand-100 text-brand-600 text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-8 animate-fade-in">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          The fair-fee alternative to Rover & Wag — waitlist now open
        </div>

        <!-- Headline -->
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight text-surface-900 font-display leading-[1.08] animate-slide-up">
          Fair care for<br/>
          <span class="text-brand-500">your best friend.</span>
        </h1>

        <!-- Subheadline -->
        <p class="mt-6 text-xl md:text-2xl text-surface-800/65 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed animate-slide-up delay-100">
          Dog boarding with transparent pricing, vetted caregivers, and fees that don't punish loyalty.
          <strong class="text-surface-900 font-semibold">Pawly takes 12% — not 40%.</strong>
        </p>

        <!-- Proof chips -->
        <div class="mt-7 flex flex-wrap gap-3 animate-slide-up delay-200">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-white border border-surface-200 text-surface-800 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full shadow-sm">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            Sitters keep 88%
          </span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-white border border-surface-200 text-surface-800 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full shadow-sm">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            No hidden booking surcharges
          </span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-white border border-surface-200 text-surface-800 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full shadow-sm">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            Background-checked caregivers
          </span>
        </div>

        <!-- CTAs -->
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 animate-slide-up delay-300">
          <a href="#waitlist" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 text-white font-bold rounded-xl transition-colors text-base shadow-lg" style="background-color: oklch(0.60 0.17 148);">
            Join the waitlist — it's free
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#caregiver" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-white text-surface-900 font-semibold rounded-xl border border-surface-200 hover:bg-surface-100 transition-colors text-base">
            Become a caregiver — keep 88%
          </a>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-surface-800/50 animate-slide-up delay-400">
          No subscription required. No credit card until you book.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       SOCIAL PROOF BAR
  ════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-14" style="background-color: oklch(0.28 0.04 248);">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
        <div class="animate-slide-up">
          <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-400 font-display">12%</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-white/60 font-medium">Total platform fee</p>
        </div>
        <div class="animate-slide-up delay-100">
          <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-400 font-display">88%</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-white/60 font-medium">Caregivers keep</p>
        </div>
        <div class="animate-slide-up delay-200">
          <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-400 font-display">$13.60</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-white/60 font-medium">More per $50 booking vs. Rover</p>
        </div>
        <div class="animate-slide-up delay-300">
          <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-400 font-display">0</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-white/60 font-medium">Hidden owner surcharges</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       THE PROBLEM — Fee Comparison
  ════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section id="problem" class="py-20 md:py-28 lg:py-32 bg-surface-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3 text-brand-500">Why Pawly exists</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-surface-900 font-display animate-slide-up">
          The pet care industry charges too much.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-surface-800/60 leading-relaxed animate-slide-up delay-100">
          On a $50 booking, Rover pays a sitter just $30.60 — and then charges the owner an additional $5.50 "booking fee" on top. That's nearly $25 vanishing from a $55.50 owner payment. Pawly splits 12% total — full stop.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Comparison table -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto animate-slide-up delay-200">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-surface-200 overflow-hidden shadow-sm">

          <!-- Header row -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-4 bg-surface-100 border-b border-surface-200">
            <div class="p-4 text-xs font-bold text-surface-800/60 uppercase tracking-widest">Platform</div>
            <div class="p-4 text-xs font-bold text-surface-800/60 uppercase tracking-widest text-center">Total fee</div>
            <div class="p-4 text-xs font-bold text-surface-800/60 uppercase tracking-widest text-center">Sitter earns on $50 booking</div>
            <div class="p-4 text-xs font-bold text-surface-800/60 uppercase tracking-widest text-center">Owner pays total</div>
          </div>

          <!-- Pawly row (highlighted) -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-4 border-b border-surface-200 bg-brand-50">
            <div class="p-5 flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-lg" aria-hidden="true">🐾</span>
              <span class="font-bold text-surface-900">Pawly</span>
              <span class="ml-1 text-xs bg-brand-500 text-white px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-semibold">US</span>
            </div>
            <div class="p-5 text-center">
              <span class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-brand-500 font-display">12%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="p-5 text-center">
              <span class="text-xl font-bold text-surface-900">$44.00</span>
            </div>
            <div class="p-5 text-center">
              <span class="text-xl font-bold text-surface-900">$50.00</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Rover row -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-4 border-b border-surface-200">
            <div class="p-5 flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-sm text-surface-800/50 font-medium">Rover</span>
            </div>
            <div class="p-5 text-center">
              <span class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-red-500 font-display">38.75%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="p-5 text-center">
              <span class="text-xl font-bold text-surface-800/70">$30.60</span>
              <p class="text-xs text-red-500 mt-0.5">$13.40 less</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-5 text-center">
              <span class="text-xl font-bold text-surface-800/70">$55.50</span>
              <p class="text-xs text-red-500 mt-0.5">+$5.50 booking fee</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Wag row -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-4">
            <div class="p-5 flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-sm text-surface-800/50 font-medium">Wag!</span>
            </div>
            <div class="p-5 text-center">
              <span class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-red-500 font-display">40%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="p-5 text-center">
              <span class="text-xl font-bold text-surface-800/70">$30.00</span>
              <p class="text-xs text-red-500 mt-0.5">$14.00 less</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-5 text-center">
              <span class="text-xl font-bold text-surface-800/70">$55.00+</span>
              <p class="text-xs text-red-500 mt-0.5">+fees vary</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-center text-xs text-surface-800/40 mt-4">
          Based on a $50 nightly booking. Rover charges owners an 11% booking fee on top of the posted rate. Wag charges 40% to sitters plus service fees to owners.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Callout -->
      <div class="mt-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto bg-brand-500 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white text-center animate-slide-up delay-300">
        <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold font-display leading-snug">
          "Your sitter earned $30.60 for watching your dog all night.<br/>
          <em class="not-italic text-brand-100">We think they deserve $44."</em>
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-white/75 text-base">
          Pawly's 12% fee is split between owner (6%) and caregiver (6%). Everyone sees exactly what they pay.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       HOW IT WORKS — 3 steps
  ════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section id="how-it-works" class="py-20 md:py-28 lg:py-32 bg-surface-100">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Simple by design</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-surface-900 font-display animate-slide-up">
          From search to tail-wags in under 5 minutes
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-surface-800/60 leading-relaxed animate-slide-up delay-100">
          No back-and-forth negotiations. No hidden checkout totals. Just find a great caregiver and book.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 relative">

        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="relative flex flex-col items-center text-center animate-slide-up">
          <!-- Number circle -->
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-brand-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-extrabold font-display shadow-lg shadow-brand-500/30 mb-6 z-10 flex-shrink-0">1</div>
          <!-- Connector (desktop) -->
          <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-7 left-[calc(50%+2rem)] w-[calc(100%-4rem)] h-0.5 z-0" style="background: repeating-linear-gradient(to right, oklch(0.73 0.17 62) 0, oklch(0.73 0.17 62) 6px, transparent 6px, transparent 14px);" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 border border-surface-200 w-full">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-brand-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 21l-5.197-5.197m0 0A7.5 7.5 0 105.196 15.803 7.5 7.5 0 0016.803 15.803z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-surface-900 font-display mb-2">Search your neighborhood</h3>
            <p class="text-surface-800/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Enter your zip code and travel dates. Browse verified caregiver profiles sorted by distance, price, and rating.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="relative flex flex-col items-center text-center animate-slide-up delay-200">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-brand-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-extrabold font-display shadow-lg shadow-brand-500/30 mb-6 z-10 flex-shrink-0">2</div>
          <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-7 left-[calc(50%+2rem)] w-[calc(100%-4rem)] h-0.5 z-0" style="background: repeating-linear-gradient(to right, oklch(0.73 0.17 62) 0, oklch(0.73 0.17 62) 6px, transparent 6px, transparent 14px);" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 border border-surface-200 w-full">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-brand-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 8.25h19.5M2.25 9h19.5m-16.5 5.25h6m-6 2.25h3m-3.75 3h15a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25V6.75A2.25 2.25 0 0019.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25v10.5A2.25 2.25 0 004.5 19.5z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-surface-900 font-display mb-2">Book with total price shown</h3>
            <p class="text-surface-800/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Pick your caregiver and confirm. The total you see — including Pawly's 6% owner fee — is the exact amount you'll pay. No checkout surprises.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="relative flex flex-col items-center text-center animate-slide-up delay-400">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-brand-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-extrabold font-display shadow-lg shadow-brand-500/30 mb-6 z-10 flex-shrink-0">3</div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 border border-surface-200 w-full">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-brand-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 15.75l5.159-5.159a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l5.159 5.159m-1.5-1.5l1.409-1.409a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l2.909 2.909m-18 3.75h16.5a1.5 1.5 0 001.5-1.5V6a1.5 1.5 0 00-1.5-1.5H3.75A1.5 1.5 0 002.25 6v12a1.5 1.5 0 001.5 1.5zm10.5-11.25h.008v.008h-.008V8.25zm.375 0a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-surface-900 font-display mb-2">Relax — get daily photo updates</h3>
            <p class="text-surface-800/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Drop off your dog and enjoy your trip. Photo check-ins land in the app twice daily so you can see your pup happy and cared for.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       FEATURES GRID
  ════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section id="features" class="py-20 md:py-28 lg:py-32 bg-surface-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Built for dog owners and caregivers</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-surface-900 font-display animate-slide-up">
          Everything you'd expect. None of the fees you don't.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

        <!-- Feature 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-surface-200 hover:border-brand-200 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200 animate-slide-up">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.036 12.322a1.012 1.012 0 010-.639C3.423 7.51 7.36 4.5 12 4.5c4.638 0 8.573 3.007 9.963 7.178.07.207.07.431 0 .639C20.577 16.49 16.64 19.5 12 19.5c-4.638 0-8.573-3.007-9.963-7.178z"/>
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-surface-900 font-display mb-2">100% transparent pricing</h3>
          <p class="text-surface-800/60 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Pawly shows owners exactly what the caregiver earns and exactly what Pawly takes — a flat 6% from each side. No one is in the dark.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-surface-200 hover:border-brand-200 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200 animate-slide-up delay-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-surface-900 font-display mb-2">Vetted, background-checked caregivers</h3>
          <p class="text-surface-800/60 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Every caregiver passes a criminal background check and a pet first-aid quiz. You read their full verification report before booking.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-surface-200 hover:border-brand-200 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200 animate-slide-up delay-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6.827 6.175A2.31 2.31 0 015.186 7.23c-.38.054-.757.112-1.134.175C2.999 7.58 2.25 8.507 2.25 9.574V18a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25h15A2.25 2.25 0 0021.75 18V9.574c0-1.067-.75-1.994-1.802-2.169a47.865 47.865 0 00-1.134-.175 2.31 2.31 0 01-1.64-1.055l-.822-1.316a2.192 2.192 0 00-1.736-1.039 48.774 48.774 0 00-5.232 0 2.192 2.192 0 00-1.736 1.039l-.821 1.316z"/>
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.5 12.75a4.5 4.5 0 11-9 0 4.5 4.5 0 019 0zM18.75 10.5h.008v.008h-.008V10.5z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-surface-900 font-display mb-2">Daily photo check-ins, guaranteed</h3>
          <p class="text-surface-800/60 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Caregivers are required to send at least 2 photo updates per day through the app. Miss one and Pawly flags the stay for review.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-surface-200 hover:border-brand-200 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200 animate-slide-up">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-brand-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 11.25v8.25a1.5 1.5 0 01-1.5 1.5H5.25a1.5 1.5 0 01-1.5-1.5v-8.25M12 4.875A2.625 2.625 0 109.375 7.5H12m0-2.625V7.5m0-2.625A2.625 2.625 0 1114.625 7.5H12m0 0V21m-8.625-9.75h18.375a1.5 1.5 0 000-3H3.375a1.5 1.5 0 000 3z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-surface-900 font-display mb-2">Loyalty rewards that actually reward you</h3>
          <p class="text-surface-800/60 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Book the same caregiver 3+ times and Pawly drops the owner fee to 4%. Book 6+ times and it drops to 2%. Your loyalty has real dollar value.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 5 -->
